text: Edmond Sandoz (8 July 1872 - 30 April 1943) was a French sports shooter. He competed in two events at the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1872 births Category:1943 deaths Category:French male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of France Category:Shooters at the 1912 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Besançon
